sourcesContent: export const aboutMeData = [ { id: 1, bio: "Hi I'm Joseph, a current 3rd year computer science student at Princeton University.\ My goal is to work on interesting technologies that will improve people's lives.\ I'm deeply interested in AI/ML, algorithms, software, cybersecurity, and mathematics.\ Feel free to contact me, I love working on cool projects!\ " }, { id: 2, bio: "In the past, I've worked a few data science roles (including one in India!), where\ I've built projects such as an options trading model and a bank-statement-based\ loan applicant scoring model." }, { id: 3, bio: "Some fun things about me: apart from being a busy busy CS student at Princeton, I love\ art, music, reading (add me on goodreads!),\ and writing (often on medium!).\ I also love trying new things, and lately, I've been learning how to dance and play the guitar!" }, { id: 4, bio: "You can check out some of my recent art below!" }, ]; /* ** bold some stufff - 3rd year student @ Princeton uni, w 7 years of programming experience - goal: work on interesting technologies that will improve people's lives - deeply interested in AI/ML, algorithms, software, cybersec, and mathematics - feel free to contact me, i love working on cool projects! - have worked a few data science roles (including one in India!), where i've built projects such as - an options trading model and a bank-statement-based applicant scoring model more about me: apart from being a busy busy cs student @ pton, i love: art music reading - link to goodreads writing - link to medium trying new things: dance */
